<br>
All by yourself, you can:<br>
1.  Get Shiny Metallic Robe and trade it for Mech. pen.<br>
2.  Get vial from Qeynos Catacombs, and fill it with ink in Guk.<br>
3.  Get snow blossoms in Oggok.<br>
4.  Get the charms in Kaesora, Overthere, and Skyfire.<br>
5.  Pick scroll in Dalnir and  key in Overthere.<br>
<br>
To a item from sky, you just need a wizard willing to take you there.<br>
<br>
Doable with single strong group (60+ average):<br>
1.  Charm in CoM<br>
2.  Verina Tomb<br>
3.  Vessel Drozlyn<br>
4.  Cazel<br>
5.  Hate.<br>
6.  Tangrin<br>
<br>
Likely will need a decent raid force (2-3 groups)<br>
1.  Chardok (not necessarily, my two guildies, lvl 65 shaman and bard, duoed the King, and could do Prince too)<br>
2.  Fear - this is the toughest.<br>
<br>
Not sure of:  Hole.  I haven't beene there since revamp, but before it was doable by single good group. <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Bregalad Alcarin</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, High Elf Coercer, Xev &lt;Legends of Westwood&gt;<br>
